We are finally live!! 😭 Thank you for all the love, I’m so so excited to finally share everything I’ve been working on. @klothelabel

A huge shout out to the wonderful ladies that helped execute my vision. @nith_yeah created exactly what I wanted with our campaign video. Our fun and beautiful models (@amaal_isse and @priyabudwal) made our work that much easier and @adorea.beauty who slayed my makeup! And of course @shotbyshiro who captured the most stunning photos in a short period of time. 🤍
